OL,3,CSpecially designed hijab created for
OL,4,Cfront line Muslim police officers
OL,6,FA specially designed hijab for female
OL,7,Ffront line Muslim police officers has
OL,8,Fgone into production in Leicestershire
OL,9,Fafter a team effort between the
OL,10,Fcounty's police force and De Montfort
OL,11,FUniversity.
OL,13,FThe design includes a quick-release
OL,14,Fsystem so the lower section detaches
OL,15,Fif it is pulled during a confrontation
OL,16,Fbetween officers and a suspect.
OL,18,FA hijab is a religious head and neck
OL,19,Fcovering which leaves the face clear.
