OL,3,CSpecially designed hijab created for
OL,4,Cfront line Muslim police officers
OL,6,FLeicestershire Police says the design
OL,7,Fteam worked with serving Muslim
OL,8,Fofficers before finalising the
OL,9,Fapproved design which is also getting
OL,10,Finterest from other emergency services
OL,11,Forganisations, including paramedics,
OL,12,Fand that it may also go on to be used
OL,13,Fin the private sector.
OL,15,FIt was originally thought of more than
OL,16,F20 years ago by Leicestershire police
OL,17,Fofficer Detective Sergeant Yassin
OL,18,FDesai.
