OL,3,CSpecially designed hijab created for
OL,4,Cfront line Muslim police officers
OL,6,FDS Desai looked at designs from around
OL,7,Fthe world before teaming up with DMU
OL,8,Fin 2022 to create a covering which
OL,9,Ffitted well, was comfortable, modest
OL,10,Fand safe.
OL,12,FDS Desai said: "It's actually taken
OL,13,Fyears to develop properly. We
OL,14,Fcompleted the combat trials at Enderby
OL,15,Fwith female officers wearing it and it
OL,16,Fheld up.
OL,18,F"The bottom part was able to detach
OL,19,Fand the officer was able to keep her
OL,20,Fdignity.
