OL,3,CSpecially designed hijab created for
OL,4,Cfront line Muslim police officers
OL,6,F"No one else has been able to make
OL,7,Fthese, only DMU. For the first time
OL,8,Fever, DMU has set up manufacturing in
OL,9,Fthe UK for this.
OL,11,F"It's amazing to think after three
OL,12,Fyears of research and development, we
OL,13,Fhave got the design of this right, and
OL,14,Fwe're taking it forward together. It's
OL,15,Fa great product, it's safe and
OL,16,Fprotects Muslim women's dignity."
