OL,4,Cfront line Muslim police officers
OL,6,FTwo student officers, Police
OL,7,FConstable's Hafsah Abba-Gana and Seher
OL,8,FNas, have both recently joined
OL,9,FLeicestershire Police and welcome the
OL,10,Fintroduction of the newly designed
OL,11,Fhijab.
OL,13,FPC Abba-Gana said: "It is reassuring
OL,14,Fto know that my faith and my role can
OL,15,Fwork hand in hand, especially as
OL,16,Fsomeone who is new to the force."
