OL,3,CSpecially designed hijab created for
OL,4,Cfront line Muslim police officers
OL,6,FInspector Marina Waka said: "It is
OL,7,Freassuring to know that this new
OL,8,Fhijab, which will be issued as part of
OL,9,Fan officer's personal protective
OL,10,Fequipment, is comfortable and safe as
OL,11,Fwell as looking smart and
OL,12,Fprofessional."
OL,14,F"I hope it will inspire other Muslim
OL,15,Fwomen to consider becoming a police
OL,16,Fofficer knowing they can wear a hijab
OL,17,Fthat protects them while fulfilling
OL,18,Ftheir religious requirements as well."
